Many Nigerians, including Billionaire Blogger, Linda Ikeji, have criticised the movie, “Coming 2 America”. The much-awaited movie hit Nigerian stream sites over the weekend and has since garnered reactions from viewers. While some Nigerian celebrities dressed up in costumes to celebrate the release of the movie, some expressed their disappointment. For Ikeji and many others, the storyline and plot left much to be desired when compared to the original movie. While some Nigerians were content with the appearance of the Nigerian Singer, Davido, in the movie, others believe he should not have been part of the cast. Here are some reactions;      